Coloration. Elytra without maculation; color of elytra brown to reddish brown; color of head and pronotum yellowish red to reddish brown, slightly lighter in color than elytra (
Fig. 3
); color of venter reddish brown, similar in color to head.

Thorax . Elytra with lateral margins slightly ascendant medially in lateral aspect (
Fig. 10
).

Distribution. Known from French Guiana and Brazil (
Fig. 23
).
